    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, \"the data overwhelmingly supports this\"? That sounds like a pretty huge claim. Aren't there lots of studies that suggest harsher sentencing actually increases recidivism or just creates a cycle of poverty in certain neighborhoods? It feels like you're dismissing the systemic impact entirely.",
